					<li id="dsq-comment-5212">
					<div id="dsq-comment-header-5212" class="dsq-comment-header">
						<cite id="dsq-cite-5212">
	http://intensedebate.com/people/dave_naffzi2081							<span id="dsq-author-user-5212">Dave Naffziger</span>
							</cite>
					</div>
					<div id="dsq-comment-body-5212" class="dsq-comment-body">
						<div id="dsq-comment-message-5212" class="dsq-comment-message"><p>The temp would not be high enough for steaks.  It could get easily as<br />high as 300+ degrees, but I think typical surface temperatures of a<br />grill are much higher.</p>
