							</cite>
					</div>
					<div id="dsq-comment-body-5318" class="dsq-comment-body">
						<div id="dsq-comment-message-5318" class="dsq-comment-message"><p>Yup, I&#039;ve smoked a turkey &#8211; 15lbs I think.  It could have been larger<br />if I recall correctly.</p>
