						<div id="dsq-comment-message-6743" class="dsq-comment-message"><p>Niki, </p>
<p>Wherever you are there should be an appliance repair shop around. You should be able to purchase some wire with high temperature insulation like what is used in an oven from them or find out where they purchase it from. I have also seen appliance wire being sold on ebay, so you can obtain it there as well.</p>
